sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Client as App Cliente
    participant Logout as /auth/logout
    participant Hosted as HostedAuthenticationAppService
    participant Master as SaasMasterDb.SsoSessions
    participant TenantDb as tenant_{id}.OAuthClients

    Client->>Client: Limpar sessão local e tokens do app
    Client-->>Browser: Redirect /auth/logout?tenant_id&post_logout_redirect_uri
    Browser->>Logout: GET /auth/logout com cookie lc_sso
    Logout->>Hosted: LogoutAsync(tenant_id, lc_sso, post_logout_redirect_uri)
    Hosted->>Master: Revogar SsoSession quando cookie existir
    Hosted->>TenantDb: Validar post_logout_redirect_uri em OAuthClient ativo
    alt Redirect autorizado
        Logout-->>Browser: Delete-Cookie lc_sso + 302 post_logout_redirect_uri
        Browser->>Client: Logout callback
    else Sem redirect autorizado
        Logout-->>Browser: Delete-Cookie lc_sso + "Logout concluido."
    end
